title: HAWKEYE (Volume 1 - Volume 3) (1983-2004) COMPLETE plus more
description:
By request, the first 3 Hawkeye volumes.

1. HAWKEYE miniseries 01-04 (1983) by Mark Gruenwald and Brett Breeding

2. HAWKEYE miniseries 01-04 (1994) by Chuck Dixon and Scott Kolins
^^^it's worth noting that this one came out immediately following the cancellation of Avengers West Coast

3. HAWKEYE: Earth's Mightiest Marksman 01 (1998)
one-shot by Tom DeFalco, Jeff Johnson and Mark Bagley

4. HAWKEYE ongoing series 01-08 (2003-2004) by Fabian Nicieza and Stefano Raffaeli, Joe Bennett, etc.

5. and I've also thrown in his first (and only, I think) 3 appearances in the Iron Man strip from TALES OF SUSPENSE in the mid-1960's, before he joined the Avengers in Avengers #16.

All credit to the scanners and the original uploader.
Please seed and share!  --STF
